law.history: Repealed 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 179, sec. 16, effective January 1, 2007. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 142, sec. 2, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 167, sec. 2, effective July 14, 2000. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 121, sec. 12, effective July 15, 1998; and ch. 357, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 148, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1996. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 451, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1994. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 54, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1990.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Business authorized by farm winery license -- Off-premise retail sales outlet in wet territory -- Use of Kentucky products -- Other permitted licenses.
